 "data": "@startuml View_Statistics_Sequence
actor \"Пользователь\" as User
participant \"Интерфейс\" as UI
participant \"StatsController\" as Controller
participant \"StatisticsService\" as StatsService
participant \"База данных\" as DB

User -> UI: Нажимает \"Статистика\"
activate User
activate UI

UI -> Controller: GET /api/statistics/overview
activate Controller

Controller -> StatsService: getUserStatistics(user_id)
activate StatsService

== Получение общей статистики ==
StatsService -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) as total_cards FROM Cards c\nJOIN Decks d ON c.deck_id = d.deck_id\nWHERE d.user_id = ?
activate DB
DB -> StatsService: total_cards
deactivate DB

StatsService -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) as studied_today FROM CardReviews\nWHERE DATE(review_date) = CURRENT_DATE\nAND card_id IN (SELECT card_id FROM Cards c\nJOIN Decks d ON c.deck_id = d.deck_id WHERE d.user_id = ?)
activate DB
DB -> StatsService: studied_today
deactivate DB

StatsService -> DB: SELECT rating, COUNT(*) as count FROM CardReviews cr\nJOIN Cards c ON cr.card_id = c.card_id\nJOIN Decks d ON c.deck_id = d.deck_id\nWHERE d.user_id = ?\nGROUP BY rating
activate DB
DB -> StatsService: rating_distribution
deactivate DB

== Получение прогресса по колодам ==
StatsService -> DB: SELECT d.name, COUNT(c.card_id) as card_count,\nCOUNT(cr.review_id) as reviewed_count\nFROM Decks d\nLEFT JOIN Cards c ON d.deck_id = c.deck_id\nLEFT JOIN CardReviews cr ON c.card_id = cr.card_id\nWHERE d.user_id = ?\nGROUP BY d.deck_id, d.name
activate DB
DB -> StatsService: deck_progress
deactivate DB

StatsService -> StatsService: calculateRetentionRate(rating_distribution)
activate StatsService

StatsService -> StatsService: generateProgressChartData(deck_progress)
activate StatsService

StatsService -> Controller: StatisticsResponse({\n total_cards: 50,\n studied_today: 15,\n retention_rate: 85.5,\n deck_progress: [...],\n charts_data: {...}\n})
deactivate StatsService

Controller -> UI: 200 OK\n{statistics_data}
deactivate Controller

UI -> UI: Отобразить дашборд статистики
UI -> UI: Построить графики прогресса
UI -> User: Показать мотивационные бейджи
deactivate UI
deactivate User
